## Unverified / Needs Documentation

These items appeared in request context or examples but were not promoted into official registry entries because the inspected documentation did not provide enough product-level evidence.

| Item | Reason | Required Documentation Before Promotion |
|---|---|---|
| Market Operations Oracle | Business product catalog explicitly lists it as not registered because no Business product evidence exists. | Business opportunity entry, owner, category, risk review and source documents. |
| MCP Business Services | Business catalog notes MCP/ACS services as future provisioning/integration risks, not a specific approved product. | Specific service definition, ACS boundary, owner and approval path. |
| Business Intelligence Services | Capability direction exists, but no specific product-level record was found. | Product candidate record and evidence source. |
| Institutional Services | Enterprise/institutional domain exists, but only sample enterprise ACS runtime has product-level evidence. | Specific opportunity or service record with source documents. |
| Generic Data Products | Data Product is a category, not a standalone opportunity. | Named data product and owner. |
| Generic Analytics Services | Analytics Product is a category, not a standalone opportunity. | Named analytics product and owner. |

