## Boundary Statement

This registry is a portfolio visibility artifact only. It does not authorize implementation, deployment, production publication, production credentials, treasury movement, wallet signing, trading, DEX swaps, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, on-chain writes, governance execution, billing execution or production readiness.

